column16: Joey Votto flies out to left fielder Jose Pirela.
Zack Cozart homers (13) on a fly ball to left center field.   Billy Hamilton scores.
Billy Hamilton grounds into a force out, first baseman Wil Myers to shortstop Dusty Coleman.   Patrick Kivlehan out at 2nd.    Billy Hamilton to 1st.
Tucker Barnhart grounds out, shortstop Dusty Coleman to first baseman Wil Myers.
Francisco Cervelli grounds out softly, third baseman Yangervis Solarte to first baseman Wil Myers.
Josh Bell singles on a line drive to shortstop Dusty Coleman, deflected by third baseman Yangervis Solarte.
David Freese grounds out, second baseman Carlos Asuaje to first baseman Wil Myers.
Andrew McCutchen called out on strikes.
Josh Harrison singles on a line drive to center fielder Manuel Margot.   Francisco Cervelli scores.    Jordy Mercer scores.    Starling Marte to 3rd.
Starling Marte walks.   Francisco Cervelli to 3rd.    Jordy Mercer to 2nd.
Adam Frazier out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Manuel Margot.   Josh Bell scores.
Starling Marte lines out to center fielder Manuel Margot.
Gerrit Cole called out on strikes.
